name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Archaeomancer
info.oracle_text: When Archaeomancer enters, return target instant or sorcery card from your graveyard to your hand.
info.flavor_text: "Words of power never disappear. They sleep, awaiting those with the will to rouse them."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Apprentice Necromancer
info.oracle_text: {B}, {T}, Sacrifice Apprentice Necromancer: Return target creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield. That creature gains haste. At the beginning of the next end step, sacrifice it.
info.flavor_text: A mage willing to dedicate his life to his craft.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Azami, Lady of Scrolls
info.oracle_text: Tap an untapped Wizard you control: Draw a card.
info.flavor_text:
"Choices belong to those with the luxuries of time and distance. We have neither. I recommend we proceed with the plan to destroy all shrines of the kami."
—Lady Azami, letter to Sensei Hisoka

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Arcanis the Omnipotent
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Draw three cards.
{2}{U}{U}: Return Arcanis the Omnipotent to its owner's hand.
info.flavor_text: He has journeyed where none have been before. Now he returns to ensure that none follow.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Bloodline Necromancer
info.oracle_text:
Lifelink
When Bloodline Necromancer enters, you may return target Vampire or Wizard creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield.
info.flavor_text: "The veil of death hides little from our kind."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Body Double
info.oracle_text: You may have Body Double enter as a copy of any creature card in a graveyard.
info.flavor_text: "I am who I pretend to be."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Comet Storm
info.oracle_text:
Multikicker {1} (You may pay an additional {1} any number of times as you cast this spell.)
Choose any target, then choose another target for each time this spell was kicked. Comet Storm deals X damage to each of them.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Commander's Sphere
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
Sacrifice Commander's Sphere: Draw a card.
info.flavor_text: It harmonizes with the essence of its master.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Command Tower
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
info.flavor_text: When defeat is near and guidance is scarce, all eyes look in one direction.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Chaos Warp
info.oracle_text: The owner of target permanent shuffles it into their library, then reveals the top card of their library. If it's a permanent card, they put it onto the battlefield.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Clone Legion
info.oracle_text: For each creature target player controls, create a token that's a copy of that creature.
info.flavor_text: Their lust for battle was so great that they didn't care their enemies wore their own faces.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Cauldron Dance
info.oracle_text:
Cast this spell only during combat.
Return target creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield. That creature gains haste. Return it to your hand at the beginning of the next end step.
You may put a creature card from your hand onto the battlefield. That creature gains haste. Its controller sacrifices it at the beginning of the next end step.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Crumbling Necropolis
info.oracle_text:
Crumbling Necropolis enters tapped.
{T}: Add {U}, {B}, or {R}.
info.flavor_text:
"They say the ruins of Sedraxis were once a shining capital in Vithia. Now it is a blight, a place to be avoided by the living."
—Olcot, Rider of Joffik

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Corpse Augur
info.oracle_text: When Corpse Augur dies, you draw X cards and you lose X life, where X is the number of creature cards in target player's graveyard.
info.flavor_text: Even when the flesh grows cold, knowledge waits in the bones for a master to release it.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Crosis's Charm
info.oracle_text:
Choose one —
• Return target permanent to its owner's hand.
• Destroy target nonblack creature. It can't be regenerated.
• Destroy target artifact.
info.flavor_text: A pretty bauble of persecution.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Curse of Disturbance
info.oracle_text:
Enchant player
Whenever enchanted player is attacked, create a 2/2 black Zombie creature token. Each opponent attacking that player does the same.
info.flavor_text: Sounds of life beckon many a restless soul.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Curse of Verbosity
info.oracle_text:
Enchant player
Whenever enchanted player is attacked, you draw a card. Each opponent attacking that player does the same.
info.flavor_text: Idle chatter beckons many an attentive ear.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Curse of Opulence
info.oracle_text:
Enchant player
Whenever enchanted player is attacked, create a Gold token. Each opponent attacking that player does the same. (A Gold token is an artifact with "Sacrifice this artifact: Add one mana of any color.")
info.flavor_text: Jingling coins beckon many an eager hand.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Dimir Aqueduct
info.oracle_text:
Dimir Aqueduct enters tapped.
When Dimir Aqueduct enters, return a land you control to its owner's hand.
{T}: Add {U}{B}.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Darksteel Ingot
info.oracle_text:
Indestructible (Effects that say "destroy" don't destroy this artifact.)
{T}: Add one mana of any color.
info.flavor_text:
"It reflects the purity of Mirrodin-that-was."
—Koth of the Hammer

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Dismal Backwater
info.oracle_text:
Dismal Backwater enters tapped.
When Dismal Backwater enters, you gain 1 life.
{T}: Add {U} or {B}.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Decree of Pain
info.oracle_text:
Destroy all creatures. They can't be regenerated. Draw a card for each creature destroyed this way.
Cycling {3}{B}{B} ({3}{B}{B}, Discard this card: Draw a card.)
When you cycle Decree of Pain, all creatures get -2/-2 until end of turn.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Exotic Orchard
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color that a land an opponent controls could produce.
info.flavor_text:
"It was a strange morning. When we awoke, we found our trees transformed. We didn't know whether to water them or polish them."
—Pulan, Bant orchardist

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Fellwar Stone
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color that a land an opponent controls could produce.
info.flavor_text:
"What do you have that I cannot obtain?"
—Mairsil, the Pretender

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Etherium-Horn Sorcerer
info.oracle_text:
{1}{U}{R}: Return Etherium-Horn Sorcerer to its owner's hand.
Cascade (When you cast this spell, exile cards from the top of your library until you exile a nonland card that costs less. You may cast it without paying its mana cost. Put the exiled cards on the bottom in a random order.)

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Evolving Wilds
info.oracle_text: {T}, Sacrifice Evolving Wilds: Search your library for a basic land card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
info.flavor_text: Without the interfering hands of civilization, nature will always shape itself to its own needs.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Go for the Throat
info.oracle_text: Destroy target nonartifact creature.
info.flavor_text: Having flesh is increasingly a liability on Mirrodin.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Galecaster Colossus
info.oracle_text: Tap an untapped Wizard you control: Return target nonland permanent you don't control to its owner's hand.
info.flavor_text: Ground bones, broken glass, and splintered shipwrecks make up the sands of his shores.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Grixis Panorama
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{1}, {T}, Sacrifice Grixis Panorama: Search your library for a basic Island, Swamp, or Mountain card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
info.flavor_text: There is no height above Grixis that is free from the stench of death.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Harbinger of the Tides
info.oracle_text:
You may cast Harbinger of the Tides as though it had flash if you pay {2} more to cast it. (You may cast it any time you could cast an instant.)
When Harbinger of the Tides enters, you may return target tapped creature an opponent controls to its owner's hand.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Havengul Lich
info.oracle_text: {1}: You may cast target creature card in a graveyard this turn. When you cast it this turn, Havengul Lich gains all activated abilities of that card until end of turn.
info.flavor_text: Fusing intelligence with the power of undeath requires inspiration of the darkest kind.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Into the Roil
info.oracle_text:
Kicker {1}{U} (You may pay an additional {1}{U} as you cast this spell.)
Return target nonland permanent to its owner's hand. If this spell was kicked, draw a card.
info.flavor_text: "Roil tide! Roil tide! Tie yourselves down!"

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Izzet Boilerworks
info.oracle_text:
Izzet Boilerworks enters tapped.
When Izzet Boilerworks enters, return a land you control to its owner's hand.
{T}: Add {U}{R}.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Izzet Chemister
info.oracle_text:
Haste
{R}, {T}: Exile target instant or sorcery card from your graveyard.
{1}{R}, {T}, Sacrifice Izzet Chemister: Cast any number of cards exiled with Izzet Chemister without paying their mana costs.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Izzet Chronarch
info.oracle_text: When Izzet Chronarch enters, return target instant or sorcery card from your graveyard to your hand.
info.flavor_text: He ensures not only whether but also when and where the lightning strikes twice.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Jwar Isle Refuge
info.oracle_text:
Jwar Isle Refuge enters tapped.
When Jwar Isle Refuge enters, you gain 1 life.
{T}: Add {U} or {B}.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Kindred Dominance
info.oracle_text: Choose a creature type. Destroy all creatures that aren't of the chosen type.
info.flavor_text: In the end, the lights fade, the land withers, and only the dead and vile remain.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Marchesa, the Black Rose
info.oracle_text:
Dethrone (Whenever this creature attacks the player with the most life or tied for most life, put a +1/+1 counter on it.)
Other creatures you control have dethrone.
Whenever a creature you control with a +1/+1 counter on it dies, return that card to the battlefield under your control at the beginning of the next end step.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Magus of the Abyss
info.oracle_text: At the beginning of each player's upkeep, destroy target nonartifact creature that player controls of their choice. It can't be regenerated.
info.flavor_text: He climbs a staircase of falling souls, fighting the continuous pull of the void.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Memory Plunder
info.oracle_text: You may cast target instant or sorcery card from an opponent's graveyard without paying its mana cost.
info.flavor_text:
"Vengeance is the echo of the victim's own crime."
—Grensch, merrow cutthroat

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Magus of the Mind
info.oracle_text: {U}, {T}, Sacrifice Magus of the Mind: Shuffle your library, then exile the top X cards, where X is one plus the number of spells cast this turn. Until end of turn, you may play lands and cast spells from among cards exiled this way without paying their mana costs.
info.flavor_text: "I'll show you what you truly desire."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Merchant of Secrets
info.oracle_text: When Merchant of Secrets enters, draw a card.
info.flavor_text: To scrape out a living in Aphetto, wizards are reduced to selling rumors, lies, forgeries, or—if they get desperate enough—the truth.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Mercurial Chemister
info.oracle_text:
{U}, {T}: Draw two cards.
{R}, {T}, Discard a card: Mercurial Chemister deals damage to target creature equal to the discarded card's mana value.
info.flavor_text: What some see as "distracted" is really "fathoming the unfathomable."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Necromantic Selection
info.oracle_text: Destroy all creatures, then return a creature card put into a graveyard this way to the battlefield under your control. It's a black Zombie in addition to its other colors and types. Exile Necromantic Selection.
info.flavor_text: It shambled from the cloud of ash and bone dust, undeterred by its own extinction.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Mirror of the Forebears
info.oracle_text:
As Mirror of the Forebears enters, choose a creature type.
{1}: Until end of turn, Mirror of the Forebears becomes a copy of target creature you control of the chosen type, except it's an artifact in addition to its other types.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Mystifying Maze
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{4}, {T}: Exile target attacking creature an opponent controls. At the beginning of the next end step, return it to the battlefield tapped under its owner's control.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Nevinyrral's Disk
info.oracle_text:
Nevinyrral's Disk enters tapped.
{1}, {T}: Destroy all artifacts, creatures, and enchantments.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Nin, the Pain Artist
info.oracle_text: {X}{U}{R}, {T}: Nin, the Pain Artist deals X damage to target creature. That creature's controller draws X cards.
info.flavor_text: "Your body is a delicate instrument that tells me truths. These devices help me 'tune' that instrument."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Nivix Guildmage
info.oracle_text:
{1}{U}{R}: Draw a card, then discard a card.
{2}{U}{R}: Copy target instant or sorcery spell you control. You may choose new targets for the copy.
info.flavor_text: "The only action worth taking is one with an unknown outcome."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Opportunity
info.oracle_text: Target player draws four cards.
info.flavor_text: "Opportunity isn't something you wait for. It's something you create."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Niv-Mizzet, the Firemind
info.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever you draw a card, Niv-Mizzet, the Firemind deals 1 damage to any target.
{T}: Draw a card.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Polymorphist's Jest
info.oracle_text: Until end of turn, each creature target player controls loses all abilities and becomes a blue Frog with base power and toughness 1/1.
info.flavor_text:
"The flies were bothering me."
—Jalira, master polymorphist

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Path of Ancestry
info.oracle_text:
Path of Ancestry enters tapped.
{T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity. When that mana is spent to cast a creature spell that shares a creature type with your commander, scry 1. (Look at the top card of your library. You may put that card on the bottom.)

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Portal Mage
info.oracle_text:
Flash
When Portal Mage enters during the declare attackers step, you may reselect which player or permanent target attacking creature is attacking. (It can't attack its controller or their permanents.)

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Puppeteer Clique
info.oracle_text:
Flying
When Puppeteer Clique enters, put target creature card from an opponent's graveyard onto the battlefield under your control. It gains haste. At the beginning of your next end step, exile it.
Persist (When this creature dies, if it had no -1/-1 counters on it, return it to the battlefield under its owner's control with a -1/-1 counter on it.)

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Rakdos Carnarium
info.oracle_text:
Rakdos Carnarium enters tapped.
When Rakdos Carnarium enters, return a land you control to its owner's hand.
{T}: Add {B}{R}.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Rakdos Charm
info.oracle_text:
Choose one —
• Exile target player's graveyard.
• Destroy target artifact.
• Each creature deals 1 damage to its controller.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Reality Shift
info.oracle_text: Exile target creature. Its controller manifests the top card of their library. (That player puts the top card of their library onto the battlefield face down as a 2/2 creature. If it's a creature card, it can be turned face up any time for its mana cost.)

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Sea Gate Oracle
info.oracle_text: When Sea Gate Oracle enters, look at the top two cards of your library. Put one of them into your hand and the other on the bottom of your library.
info.flavor_text: "The secret entrance should be near."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Shadowmage Infiltrator
info.oracle_text:
Fear (This creature can't be blocked except by artifact creatures and/or black creatures.)
Whenever Shadowmage Infiltrator deals combat damage to a player, you may draw a card.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Sol Ring
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add {C}{C}.
info.flavor_text: Lost to time is the artificer's art of trapping light from a distant star in a ring of purest gold.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Shifting Shadow
info.oracle_text:
Enchant creature
Enchanted creature has haste and "At the beginning of your upkeep, destroy this creature. Reveal cards from the top of your library until you reveal a creature card. Put that card onto the battlefield and attach Shifting Shadow to it, then put all other cards revealed this way on the bottom of your library in a random order."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Silumgar's Command
info.oracle_text:
Choose two —
• Counter target noncreature spell.
• Return target permanent to its owner's hand.
• Target creature gets -3/-3 until end of turn.
• Destroy target planeswalker.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Spelltwine
info.oracle_text: Exile target instant or sorcery card from your graveyard and target instant or sorcery card from an opponent's graveyard. Copy those cards. Cast the copies if able without paying their mana costs. Exile Spelltwine.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Serendib Sorcerer
info.oracle_text: {T}: Target creature other than Serendib Sorcerer has base power and toughness 0/2 until end of turn.
info.flavor_text: "Even a dragon is humble as a kitten if it thinks itself a slave."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Swiftwater Cliffs
info.oracle_text:
Swiftwater Cliffs enters tapped.
When Swiftwater Cliffs enters, you gain 1 life.
{T}: Add {U} or {R}.

info.oracle_text: {T}: Add {C}{C}. Activate only if you control five or more lands.
info.flavor_text:
"When gods become apathetic, the people will worship anyone who answers their pleas."

Skip your draw step.
At the beginning of your upkeep, look at the top three cards of your library. Put one of them into your hand and the rest into your graveyard.
{B}, {T}, Exile X cards from your graveyard: Target creature gets -X/-X until end of turn.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Terramorphic Expanse
info.oracle_text: {T}, Sacrifice Terramorphic Expanse: Search your library for a basic land card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)

info.flavor_text: All suns must set.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)

Vivid Crag enters tapped with two charge counters on it.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Vivid Creek
info.oracle_text:
Vivid Creek enters tapped with two charge counters on it.
{T}: Add {U}.
{T}, Remove a charge counter from Vivid Creek: Add one mana of any color.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Unstable Obelisk
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{7}, {T}, Sacrifice Unstable Obelisk: Destroy target permanent.
info.flavor_text: Its collapse is like the lashing out of a long-dead civilization that resents being forgotten.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Vela the Night-Clad
info.oracle_text:
Intimidate (This creature can't be blocked except by artifact creatures and/or creatures that share a color with it.)
Other creatures you control have intimidate.
Whenever Vela the Night-Clad or another creature you control leaves the battlefield, each opponent loses 1 life.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Vivid Marsh
info.oracle_text:
Vivid Marsh enters tapped with two charge counters on it.
{T}: Add {B}.
{T}, Remove a charge counter from Vivid Marsh: Add one mana of any color.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Vindictive Lich
info.oracle_text:
When Vindictive Lich dies, choose one or more. Each mode must target a different player.
• Target opponent sacrifices a creature.
• Target opponent discards two cards.
• Target opponent loses 5 life.
info.flavor_text: Heart, mind, soul—weapons all.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Worn Powerstone
info.oracle_text:
Worn Powerstone enters tapped.
{T}: Add {C}{C}.
info.flavor_text: Even a fragment of a powerstone contains within it not just energy, but space—vast dimensions trapped in fragile crystal.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Kess, Dissident Mage
info.oracle_text:
Flying
Once during each of your turns, you may cast an instant or sorcery spell from your graveyard. If a spell cast this way would be put into your graveyard, exile it instead.
info.flavor_text: "Loss has no meaning here. You cannot take from those who have nothing."

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Mairsil, the Pretender
info.oracle_text:
When Mairsil, the Pretender enters, you may exile an artifact or creature card from your hand or graveyard and put a cage counter on it.
Mairsil, the Pretender has all activated abilities of all cards you own in exile with cage counters on them. You may activate each of those abilities only once each turn.

name: Arcane Wizardry (Commander 2017 Precon Decklist)
info.name: Inalla, Archmage Ritualist
info.oracle_text:
Eminence — Whenever another nontoken Wizard you control enters, if Inalla, Archmage Ritualist is in the command zone or on the battlefield, you may pay {1}. If you do, create a token that's a copy of that Wizard. The token gains haste. Exile it at the beginning of the next end step.
Tap five untapped Wizards you control: Target player loses 7 life.

info.name: Copy
info.oracle_text: (This token can be used to represent a token that's a copy of a permanent.)

info.name: Darksteel Hydra
info.oracle_text:
Indestructible
Darksteel Hydra enters with X oil counters on it.
Darksteel Hydra's power and toughness are each equal to twice the number of oil counters on it.
When Darksteel Hydra enters, conjure a card named Darksteel Ingot and a card named Darksteel Plate into your hand.

info.name: Gold
info.oracle_text: Sacrifice this artifact: Add one mana of any color.

info.name: Manifest
info.oracle_text:
